      "review_summary": "The PR changes Claude live-session `can_use_tool` handling and spawn tests so restrictive ask-enabled exec policies return `behavior: \"ask\"` instead of `behavior: \"deny\"`.\n\nPR surface: Source +15, Tests -3. Total +12 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main responds to restrictive Claude `can_use_tool` requests with `behavior: \"deny\"`, matching the linked no-operator-prompt report. I did not run a live Claude CLI session in this read-only review.",
